(34, '6d629026-5851-4ed7-a68b-0c7fc2817c97', 'New Job Assignment by FixMaster', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Dear {firstname} {lastname},</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">A new job request is available for execution near you and <b>FixMaster</b> has assigned you specifically for this purpose. Kindly login to your account to ACCEPT the job NOW!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 14.98px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Please click {url}</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 14.98px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">&nbsp;to view details and accept the job request.</span><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 14.98px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Your job rating counts! Remember to request a rating and review on all completed diagnoses and job repairs completed.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Dear {firstname} {lastname},\n\n\n\nA new job request is available for execution near you and FixMaster has assigned you specifically for this purpose. Kindly login to your account to ACCEPT the job NOW!\n\nPlease click {url} to view details and accept the job reques